1. *Vratite* mi knjigu (Return the book to me). 
2. Oni su nam *vratili* novac (They returned the money to us). 
3. Ja ću vam *vratiti* dug (I will repay the debt to you). 
4. Ona je *vratila* svoju sestru kući (She returned her sister home). 
5. On će *vratiti* svoju ljubav (He will return his love). 
6. Oni su nam *vratili* sreću (They returned happiness to us).